KTS is a web application for booking tickets for students in some institute
Users have there own front end to booking tickets and view QR contained
Admin have his own frontend to manage employees, routes, buses

KTS application contained 3 services 
    1. admin - frontend for admin
    2. user - front end for a user
    3. backend







First Start backend service - use start-backend.sh
______________________________________________________________
docker build -t kts-backend -f ./backend/Dockerfile ./backend

docker run -d --rm \
 --name backend \
 -p 4000:4000 \
 --env-file ./backend/.env \
 kts-backend_
 _____________________________________________________________

replace environment variables in backend/.env file 

______________________________________________________________
CLOUDINARY_URL=
EMAIL_HOST=
EMAIL_PASS=
EMAIL_USER=
JWT_SECRET=
MONGO_URI=
______________________________________________________________












Then start user and admin front-ends - user start-user.sh and start-admin.sh

start-user.sh

_______________________________________________________________
source .env

docker build -t kts-user \
--build-arg VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=$VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY \
-f ./user/Dockerfile \
./user

docker run -d --rm \
 --name user \
 -p 3001:80 \
 kts-user
________________________________________________________________

.env file should contain google maps id
________________________________________________________________
export VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
________________________________________________________________

start-admin.sh
________________________________________________________________
source .env

docker build -t kts-admin \
--build-arg VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=$VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY \
-f ./admin/Dockerfile \
./admin

docker run -d --rm \
 --name admin \
 -p 3000:80 \
 kts-admin
________________________________________________________________

.env file should contain google maps id
________________________________________________________________
export VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
________________________________________________________________